# Intito MasterFlow impact analysis for integrations
# Purpose: Evaluate integration contracts affected by a version diff.
# Sources:
# - IMF.C.Diff
# - Integration/export-import contract definitions
# - IMF.C.Impact
# Parameters:
# - pPrefix: Naming prefix for Intito MasterFlow control objects. Default 'IMF'.
# - pDimensionCode: Managed dimension code.
# - pVersionId: Existing work version.
# Prolog:
# - Resolve diff scope for the selected version.
# Metadata:
# - Identify external interfaces depending on keys, paths, or attributes.
# Data:
# - Classify downstream integration breakage risk.
# Epilog:
# - Write integration-domain findings to IMF.C.Impact.

sPrefix = Trim(pPrefix);
If(sPrefix @= '');
  sPrefix = 'IMF';
EndIf;

